    #   • _ug_card(key)    — returns a single section accordion card
    #
    # Layout: 2-column on ≥1100px (content left, sidebar right, sticky)
    #         Single column on narrow screens (sidebar collapses below content)
    # ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

