                ("Set Duration", "Minimum 2 minutes for reliable results. Use 5+ minutes for pre-launch validation."),
                ("Read P95 latency", "P95 < 500ms = excellent. P95 < 1000ms = acceptable. P95 > 2000ms = users will abandon."),
                ("Check error rate", "Error rate > 1% under load = server saturation. Find the VU count where errors start."),
